text: Ðis sinte ða gewitnisse of þam lande ðe Alfric paz bohte at frewines laue at hire on paules stret, Waltere restolles sune, Alfred preost, Adam preost, Alger liflædes, sune Waltere, and Osbern Alworð wuna portr Godwi, Seiner and suelger, Liword lozel, Alger teonnes sune, Rocgere <sibus>.
Ðis sinte ða gewitnisse of ðam wiman leduue ialdit and of Ieleire, reinfrei þæt is Gedmer, Acuic, and Alger, Lifleð, Alwne, seuara wif, adeleg.
Ða sint þage gewitnisse of þam lande þe Alfric bohte at Ailworde þat is walword at iacobes circa: Siword and Swæin, Giðwine, Heisucg Alword se scinr and oþre genoge.
And Særle and Pain namen þæt toll.
Of þam lande bute gestete þe Alfric bohte at Ricerde.
Ðis sint þage gewitnesse Osbern, Algerfiliusand <ware> scolfues sunu <Rob> se <ce>, and Alger lifflæd, Ralf se nuueuð and Ascetild and Godric puddiges and oþre genoge, and Gilebert nam þæt toll.
Of þam lande a martines stræt þa Alfric bohte at Ragenilde, Gewitnisse and oþre genoge and Guldebert nam þæt toll.
